    <b><font face="arial" color="#003399">proftpd.org update</font></b>
    <br />
    <font size="-1">[<i>17/Sept/2001</i>]</font>

    <blockquote><font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1">
     The core proftpd.org server appears to be having problems and the admin
