     www.proftpd.org/net and ftp.proftpd.org to one of the existing mirrors. 
     At the moment bugs.proftpd.org and mail delivery is unaffected, however
     the mailing list archives are offline.  We will update this site once
     more details are available.
     - <em>hamster</em>
    </font></blockquote>

    <blockquote><font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1">
